text: Benjámin Vadnai (born 30 December 1995) is a Hungarian competitive sailor. He competed at the 2016 Summer Olympics in Rio de Janeiro, in the men's Laser class. ==References== Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:Hungarian sailors Category:Olympic sailors of Hungary Category:Sailors at the 2016 Summer Olympics – Laser
